		<title>Contraline Raises $92.5 Million Series B to Advance NES/T Male Contraceptive Development</title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/contraline-raises-92-5m/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Clinton]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 14:50:30 +0000</pubDate>
